Actions.Text: REFERRED TO INVESTIGATIONS AND GOVERNMENT OPERATIONS
REFERRED TO INVESTIGATIONS AND GOVERNMENT OPERATIONS

Title: Eliminates any yearly fees associated with the use of docks on public waterways
Summary: Relates to eliminating any yearly fees associated with the use of docks on public waterways; application fees shall be subject to the approval of the director of the budget and shall not exceed one hundred dollars.
LawCode: Amd ยง75, Pub Lds L
ActClause: AN ACT to amend the public lands law, in relation to eliminating any yearly fees associated with the use of docks on public waterways
